                        <interp inst="t18370814-name-645" type="given" value="HECTOR"></interp>HECTOR ESSEX</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a pawnbroker, at Islington. I sold the prisoner two watches, one on the 4th of July, and another on the 11th.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
